### 4. API Management Service (Spring WebMVC)

#### Key Dependencies
- `spring-boot-starter-web`
- `spring-boot-starter-data-jpa`
- `spring-boot-starter-security`
- `spring-boot-starter-validation`
- `flyway-core` + `flyway-database-postgresql`
- `common` module

#### Database Schema (`V1__init_schema.sql`)

```sql
CREATE TABLE plans (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
    name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,        -- FREE, BASIC, PRO, ENTERPRISE
    requests_per_minute INT NOT NULL,
    monthly_quota BIGINT NOT NULL,
    price_cents INT DEFAULT 0,
    webhook_enabled BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);

CREATE TABLE registered_apis (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
    owner_email VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    target_url VARCHAR(500) NOT NULL,         -- original API URL
    proxy_path VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE NOT NULL,  -- unique proxy slug
    is_active BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW(),
    updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);

CREATE TABLE api_keys (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
    key_hash VARCHAR(64) UNIQUE NOT NULL,     -- SHA-256 hash
    key_prefix VARCHAR(8) NOT NULL,           -- first 8 chars for display
    registered_api_id UUID REFERENCES registered_apis(id),
    plan_id UUID REFERENCES plans(id),
    is_active BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE,
    disabled_reason VARCHAR(255),
    webhook_url VARCHAR(500),
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);

-- Seed default plans
INSERT INTO plans (name, requests_per_minute, monthly_quota, webhook_enabled) VALUES
    ('FREE', 10, 1000, FALSE),
    ('BASIC', 60, 50000, FALSE),
    ('PRO', 300, 500000, TRUE),
    ('ENTERPRISE', 1000, 5000000, TRUE);
```

#### [NEW] REST Endpoints

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/api/v1/apis` | Register a new API |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/apis` | List user's registered APIs |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/apis/{id}` | Get API details |
| `PUT` | `/api/v1/apis/{id}` | Update API config |
| `DELETE` | `/api/v1/apis/{id}` | Deactivate API |
| `POST` | `/api/v1/apis/{id}/keys` | Generate API key |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/apis/{id}/keys` | List keys for an API |
| `DELETE` | `/api/v1/keys/{id}` | Revoke API key |
| `GET` | `/api/v1/plans` | List available plans |
| `PUT` | `/api/v1/keys/{id}/plan` | Change key's plan |
| `GET` | `/internal/api-configs/{apiKeyHash}` | Internal: get config for Gateway |
| `PUT` | `/internal/keys/{id}/disable` | Internal: disable key (quota exceeded) |

#### [NEW] `ApiRegistrationService.java`
- Generates unique `proxyPath` slugs
- Returns full proxy URL: `http://gateway:8080/proxy/{proxyPath}/`
- API key generation: generates random 32-byte key, stores SHA-256 hash, returns raw key once

#### [NEW] `SecurityConfig.java`
- `/api/v1/**` endpoints secured with basic auth or JWT (configurable)
- `/internal/**` endpoints secured with shared secret header (`X-Internal-Secret`)
- `/actuator/health` public

